description: The Flagship ETH Morpho vault curated by B.Protocol and Block Analitica is intended to optimize risk-adjusted interest earned from blue-chip LST and stablecoin collateral markets. The Flagship ETH vault also serves as a pre-deposit vault for Relend Network.

The Vaults risk strategy will follow the CORE framework where Gauntlet curates deposits to balance security and yield to provide a moderate risk profile and competitive APY for USDT0 suppliers.

Gauntlet uses its expertise to actively manage allocations, targeting diverse markets with stable yields above the Lido staking rate. Deposit into the vault via the Index Coop App Site for optimal performance.
